title: Freeze warning issued for early Monday in Northeast Ohio
text:
Freeze warning issued for early Monday in Northeast Ohio 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
The National Weather Service has issued a freeze warning that will be in effect early Monday in counties along Lake Erie....
